    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Phylogenetic analysis of six SARS-CoV-2 genomes collected from the Comoros islands confirmed local circulation of the 501Y.V2 variant of concern during the country\u2019s first major SARS-CoV-2 wave in January 2021. These findings demonstrate the importance of SARS-CoV-2 genomic surveillance and have implications for ongoing COVID-19 control strategies on the islands.</jats:p>\n                <jats:sec>\n                  <jats:title>Article summary line</jats:title>\n                  <jats:p>Circulation of SARS-CoV-2 501Y.V2 variant of concern in the Comoros Islands during a major COVID-19 infection wave in January 2021</jats:p>\n                </jats:sec>",
